<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu cāḷukyavikra
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mavarśada nālva<unclear>tēḻe</unclear>neya <unclear>pla</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>va sauvacarada jēṭṭa suddha bidigeya
<lb n="4"/>Ādivāra dakṣiṇāyanasaṁkramaṇa vyatī pātadaṁ<unclear>du</unclear>
<lb n="5"/>śrīmanu mahāmaṇḍaḷēsvara permmāḍi yarasa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>yaka<unclear>ṁ</unclear> śrīmatu <unclear>dēva</unclear>ra ba(ṁ)mmaya nāyaka <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>yaṁ dēvulada tanna pūje vrittiyo <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>ṟeya mūlasthāna gōviṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>rgge kōṭeya <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>beḷugalliṁ paḍuvalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>ta sarvvanamasyavā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/>śrīmanu mahāmaṇḍa <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> <note n="253-1">The lower portion of the stone is broken off and missing.</note>
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="13"/>priyadi<unclear>ṁ</unclear>di ntida neydekā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>va puruṣaṁ gāyu<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="15"/>mahāśrīyu makku<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="16"/>yidaṁ kāyade kāyva
<lb n="17"/>pāpige kurukṣētradoḷu
<lb n="18"/>vāraṇāsi<supplied reason="omitted">yo</supplied>ḷu kōṭimunīṁ
<lb n="19" break="no"/>draraṁ kavileyaṁ vēdāḍhyaraṁ
<lb n="20"/>kondu doṁdeyasaṁ sārggu yi
<lb n="21"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> kuru<note n="253-1">The lower portion of</note>
</p>

